---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Button from '../components/Button.astro';
---

<Layout title="LogComply - Sua jornada em conformidade começa aqui.">
  <div class="w-full min-h-screen bg-[#0B1726] text-white">
    <Header />


	<div class="relative w-full flex justify-center">
      <img src="/painel.png" alt="Painel" class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[600px] object-cover opacity-60 pointer-events-none select-none z-0" style="height: 600px;" />
      <div class="absolute top-0 left-0 w-full h-[600px] bg-[#0B1726] opacity-60 z-0"></div>
      <main class="relative z-10 flex flex-col items-center pt-20 md:pt-32 px-4">
        {/* Hero Section */}
        <section class="max-w-3xl w-full text-center">
          <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold leading-tight">
            Seus voos em conformidade começam aqui.
          </h1>
          <p class="mt-4 text-lg md:text-xl text-[#4FC3F7] font-medium">
            Valide, Registre, Decole em segurança.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex justify-center gap-4">
            <Button href="/register">Comece agora</Button>
            <Button href="/demo" variant="secondary">Ver demonstração</Button>
          </div>
        </section>

        {/* Funcionalidades-chave */}
        <section class="w-full max-w-5xl mt-20">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-6 text-left">Nossas Ferramentas</h2>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4">
            <div class="bg-[#14213D] rounded-lg p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
              <img src="/assets/astro.svg" alt="JorneyComply" class="w-10 h-10 mb-2" />
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1 w-full text-center">Validação de Jornada</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm text-center"></p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#14213D] rounded-lg p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
              <img src="/assets/astro.svg" alt="Em Breve" class="w-10 h-10 mb-2" />
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1 w-full text-center">Em Breve</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm text-center"></p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#14213D] rounded-lg p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
              <img src="/assets/astro.svg" alt="Em Breve" class="w-10 h-10 mb-2" />
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1 w-full text-center">Em Breve</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm text-center"></p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-[#14213D] rounded-lg p-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center">
              <img src="/assets/astro.svg" alt="Em Breve" class="w-10 h-10 mb-2" />
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-lg mb-1 w-full text-center">Em Breve</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm text-center"></p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="#" class="block mt-4 text-[#4FC3F7] hover:underline text-sm">Ver todos os módulos</a>
        </section>

        {/* Demonstração em vídeo */}
        <section class="w-full max-w-5xl mt-16 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-start">
          <div>
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold mb-4">Demonstração em vídeo</h2>
            <div class="bg-[#14213D] rounded-lg p-4 flex flex-col items-center">
              <div class="w-full aspect-video bg-[#1A263B] rounded flex items-center justify-center">
                <svg width="48" height="48" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="12" fill="#4FC3F7"/><polygon points="10,8 16,12 10,16" fill="#0B1726"/></svg>
              </div>
              <span class="mt-2 text-gray-400 text-xs">1:39</span>
            </div>
            <blockquote class="mt-6 text-gray-300 italic text-sm">
              “O LogComply virou copiloto silencioso. Eu voo tranquila.”<br/>
              <span class="not-italic font-medium text-xs text-gray-500">Instrutor chefe: 50XP</span>
            </blockquote>
            <blockquote class="mt-4 text-gray-300 italic text-sm">
              “Hoje contolo manutenco. Jornada e diário com um clique.”<br/>
              <span class="not-italic font-medium text-xs text-gray-500">Gerenne lasnic, operadora ffteácara</span>
            </blockquote>
          </div>
          <div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 text-left text-gray-300 text-sm mt-2">
              <li>✔️ Redução de erros regulatórios/softcveio</li>
              <li>✔️ Economia de backoff fice elime sosn</li>
              <li>✔️ Confidenciá.com ANACropeicaãoetacúra</li>
              <li>✔️ Integração com ADS-B <span class="text-[#4FC3F7]">Faça mais</span></li>
            </ul>
            <div class="mt-8">
              <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Depoimentos</h3>
              <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 items-center">
                <span class="bg-[#1A263B] rounded px-3 py-1 text-xs flex items-center gap-2"><svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="12" fill="#4FC3F7"/></svg>API Restful</span>
                <span class="bg-[#1A263B] rounded px-3 py-1 text-xs flex items-center gap-2"><svg width="18" height="18" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><rect width="18" height="18" fill="#4FC3F7"/></svg>ADS B Exchange</span>
                <span class="bg-[#1A263B] rounded px-3 py-1 text-xs flex items-center gap-2">Flight Aware</span>
                <span class="bg-[#1A263B] rounded px-3 py-1 text-xs flex items-center gap-2">EASA Logbook</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>

        {/* Call to Action Final */}
        <section class="w-full max-w-3xl mt-16 text-center">
          <h2 class="text-xl md:text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Pronto para digitalizar tudo o que antes era planilha e papel?</h2>
          <Button href="/register">Comece agora</Button>
        </section>
      </main>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  body {
    margin: 0;
  }
</style>